    "headline": "Thunes Joins Swift and Visa as a Global Cross-Border Payments Leader",
    "summary": "Thunes, the Smart Superhighway to move money around the world, has been named a top three global leader in the cross-border payments sector in a report by Juniper Research. In the report's 2026 'Competitor Leaderboard', Thunes secured its position alongside industry giants Swift and Visa, scoring particularly highly in the breadth of solutions, customer deployments, innovation, and future business prospects categories.",
